%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%

sequenceDiagram
autonumber

actor ADMIN as Admin / IBX BP
actor COE as COE Head
participant UI as Innovation UI
participant BFF as Innovation BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant SERVICE as Innovation Service
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS Read schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}
participant NS as Notification Service
participant CACHE as Redis

ADMIN ->> UI: Open Sent Back Portfolio / Cohort
UI ->> BFF: Load editable entity
BFF ->> SERVICE: getEditableEntity(entityId, entityType)
SERVICE ->> READDB: Get details, comments, ringi, evaluation model
READDB -->> SERVICE: Editable data with review comments
SERVICE -->> BFF: Entity payload
BFF -->> UI: Render editable form

ADMIN ->> UI: Correct details and click Resubmit
UI ->> BFF: resubmitEntity(entityId, entityType)

BFF ->> ORCH: startResubmissionWorkflow(entityId, entityType)

ORCH ->> SERVICE: validateResubmission(entityId, entityType)
SERVICE ->> READDB: Validate status = Sent Back
SERVICE ->> READDB: Validate required details complete

alt Validation Failed
    SERVICE -->> ORCH: Validation errors
    ORCH -->> BFF: Return errors
    BFF -->> UI: Show validation messages
else Validation Passed
    ORCH ->> SERVICE: resubmitEntity(entityId, entityType)
    SERVICE ->> PRIMARYDB: UPDATE portfolio/cohort SET status='Review'
    SERVICE ->> PRIMARYDB: INSERT workflow_audit(action='RESUBMIT', stage='Review')
    SERVICE -->> ORCH: Resubmitted

    ORCH ->> KAFKA: Publish InnovationEntityResubmitted
    ORCH ->> CACHE: Invalidate COE/Admin lists

    KAFKA ->> NS: Consume resubmission event
    NS ->> READDB: Fetch COE Head recipients
    NS ->> PRIMARYDB: INSERT notification records

    ORCH -->> BFF: Resubmission success
    BFF -->> UI: Show Submitted for Review
    NS -->> COE: Notify resubmission for review
end